{"tid":1435123,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜丹尼爾再爆「一周約會1次志效」 D社為他延遲3次報導！","createTime":"2019-08-09T03:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:38:52.000Z","uid":74065,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a140f27e6e90719caefc92968d6c11ba90380705","tid":1435123,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:12:45.000Z","msg":"南韓偶像姜丹尼爾5日認愛TWICE隊長志效，超人氣偶像CP誕生，受到全球粉絲注目。拍到兩人約會直擊的媒體《Dispatch》被發現，第一次打算刊出報導的日期是7月20日，卻因為不明原因，報導直到8月5日才曝光，對此，D社在8日認了確實是考慮到姜丹尼爾回歸在即，才會把新聞延到5日刊出，一共延了3次。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4293/d4293712.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4293%2Fd4293712.jpg&h=03b94a52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼姜丹尼爾、志效被爆料一周約會一次。（圖／翻攝自MBC）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4293/d4293714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4293%2Fd4293714.jpg&h=c5d643d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據《Section TV 演藝通信》8日播岀的內容，姜丹尼爾與志效愛得熱烈，約會期間至少一周見一次，但礙於兩人都是偶像的身份，因此主要都在家裡約會，鮮少邁出家門，7月25日、8月1日都是雙方結束行程後，偷偷見面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4293/d4293715.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4293%2Fd4293715.jpg&h=097c434b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼撰寫姜丹尼爾戀愛報導的吳姓記者親口承認，報導推遲了3次刊出。（圖／翻攝自MBC）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4293/d4293716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4293%2Fd4293716.jpg&h=87f344a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外，節目訪問到《Dispatch》記者，對方坦言，確實是考慮到姜丹尼爾7月25日回歸，因此報導延到8月1日出，不巧，他當天又有見面會，於是再把報導延期到8月2日，殊不知，8月2日礙於日韓貿易戰升溫，最後才決定在8月5日曝光新聞，一共推遲了3次報導刊出的日期。"},{"pid":"aeb2a5724a7c925fe2362049ffa11798a336f962","tid":1435123,"uid":43061,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 姜舟尼爾"},{"pid":"97b034e7e8b9a4b73a59663d2c478370127e7f08","tid":1435123,"uid":205928,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:14:04.000Z","msg":"mola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e079a8f91ccfb27700690b4cc198add1e28935f5","tid":1435123,"uid":167880,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:18:25.000Z","msg":"在家中約會？！實扑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f897e538035579622a97b1613256e7705325f484","tid":1435123,"uid":294614,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:18:57.000Z","msg":"8.9       機場萬人接機<br />\n開始時間： 2019年8月9日下午1 點起<br />\n地點 ： 一號客運大樓機場接機大堂<br />\n1. 不申請不反對通知書<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 和平靜坐，不衝擊不破壞不入禁區</span><br />\n3. Be water<br />\n4. 促政府答應五大訴求<br />\n5. 停止暴力打壓示威遊行<br />\n少你一個真係少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日1:00 機場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xGQPZ5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxGQPZ5c.png&h=7a7f7945&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2d28a0539be94cb8809546702b28fc319aaea78","tid":1435123,"uid":193951,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:18:59.000Z","msg":"d社算係咁啦 等你comeback埋先爆料"},{"pid":"64f58719d3c61150cc04e6d8b4f2e96842431888","tid":1435123,"uid":60256,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"一周內射一次"},{"pid":"e23ad9b59a71397dac33b90759cc706f7b5fd4d9","tid":1435123,"uid":137569,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:20:41.000Z","msg":"志效對奶應該有唔少咖哩雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6954133654e15fd12b56ae3830749c2168db67","tid":1435123,"uid":48317,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"一個禮拜先屌一次<br />\n咁忍得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"